title: Primate Info Net, World Primates, World, 2008
name: Primate Info Net, World Primates, World, 2008
description: This is a dataset that displays in what countries each species of primate can be found. Some species have be lumped together, such as all Lemurs, since all lemurs are only found in Madagascar. There is also an attribute which displays how many species are found in each country.

author.source: Primate Info Net, National Primate Research Center
